arkup": "markdown", "html": "<p>When terminating a [simulator] constellation, the operation times-out if the machine has been terminated previously in the AWS console.</p>\n<p>This is because for the instance dissapears from AWS after 20 minutes or so, and the terminate operation expects it.</p>\n<p>The termination should finish early if AWS reports that the machine(s) does not exist.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-12-10T19:03:11.056132+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-12-10T19:03:11.056132+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 176}